11#ifndef API_AUDIO_CODECS_OPUS_AUDIO_DECODER_OPUS_H_
12#define API_AUDIO_CODECS_OPUS_AUDIO_DECODER_OPUS_H_

14#include <memory>
15#include <vector>
16
17#include "absl/types/optional.h"
18#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_codec_pair_id.h"
19#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_decoder.h"
20#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_format.h"

23namespace webrtc {
24
25// Opus decoder API for use as a template parameter to
26// CreateAudioDecoderFactory<...>().
27struct RTC_EXPORT AudioDecoderOpus {
28 struct Config {
29 bool IsOk() const; // Checks if the values are currently OK.
30 int sample_rate_hz = 48000;
31 int num_channels = 1;
32 };
33 static absl::optional<Config> SdpToConfig(const SdpAudioFormat& audio_format);
34 static void AppendSupportedDecoders(std::vector<AudioCodecSpec>* specs);
35 static std::unique_ptr<AudioDecoder> MakeAudioDecoder(
36 Config config,
37 absl::optional<AudioCodecPairId> codec_pair_id = absl::nullopt);
38};
39
40} // namespace webrtc
41
42#endif // API_AUDIO_CODECS_OPUS_AUDIO_DECODER_OPUS_H_
